Class XMLIncludedAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docgene.model.XMLIncludedAPI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParagraphElement, ParagraphElementParent, StyledElement

    public class XMLIncludedAPI
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParagraphElement, ParagraphElementParent
    A general included API link. This is used for both the <javaAPI> and <pythonAPI> tags.
